Viduvaka viswaasamutho niluvudi.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Sathkaryamulannitanu saphaluguchu,
Santhoshimpa prabhu sarvaamulo,
Thandritho naadhuvu thaginatluga.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Dhaivaathma suthulu devunni vaarasulu,
